start_time = current_timestamp_in_millis()
ax_client = AxClient()
ax_client.create_experiment(parameters=[{'name': 'x', 'type': 'range',
    'bounds': [-5.0, 10.0]}, {'name': 'y', 'type': 'range', 'bounds': [0.0,
    15.0]}], minimize=True)
params, idx = ax_client.get_next_trial()
ax_client.complete_trial(trial_index=idx, raw_data=1.0, metadata={
    'start_time': start_time, 'end_time': current_timestamp_in_millis()})
dat = ax_client.experiment.fetch_data().df
self.assertGreater(dat['end_time'][0], dat['start_time'][0])
